dcterms:description: The PSD database contains detailed information on the electricity consumption of several hundred households, mostly from Texas. The available information consists of the electricity consumption of each electrical appliance in the household, including electric cars and the current needed for their charging.

dcterms:description: The NHTS data contain information on travels performed by US households. For each household, the first travel by car in the day starting at home and the last travel by car in the day ending at home are recorded, along with the day of the week.
dcterms:title: National Household Transportation Survey (NHTS)

dcterms:description: Eurostat data provides statistics on passenger cars in the EU, including the number of registered cars and their distribution across member states.
dcterms:title: Eurostat data
